n difficulty, though a concern, is less severe than the outright uncooperativeness reported for Candidate\u202fB or the poor teamwork traits of Candidate\u202fD. Candidate\u202fA lacks essential stress\u2011handling data.\nTherefore, based on the complete set of attributes we have, I consider **Candidate\u202fC** the strongest overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
